“我是逃难的”，她代购防疫物资为名诈骗百万元被捕。
"I'm on the run," she was arrested for swindling a million dollars for a vaccination campaign.
澎湃新闻                      。
The news is roaring.
澎湃新闻。
The news is roaring.
有内涵的时政新媒体。
Connotation of the new political media.
澎湃新闻记者 朱奕奕“知道为什么抓你吗？”“知道的。
"Do you know why you're being arrested?" "I know.
”“家在杨浦，你怎么会到这里（宝山）来！”“我是过来‘逃难’的！”上述民警和犯罪嫌疑人的对话发生在抓捕现场。
"Home in Yangpu, how did you come here [Baoshan]!" "I'm here to escape!" The conversation between the police and the suspect took place at the scene of the arrest.
2月25日，上海杨浦警方在宝山区罗店镇出租屋内，将犯罪嫌疑人周某抓获，其涉嫌以售卖抗疫用品为名实施电信网络诈骗。
February 25, Shanghai Yangpu police in Baoshan Luodian Town rental housing, suspects Zhou Mou, suspected of selling anti-epidemic supplies in the name of the network fraud.
当民警抓获周某时，其竟把自己的潜逃说成是“逃难”。
When the police captured Zhou Mou, it actually said their abscond is "flight."
抓捕现场。
Arrest scene.
本文图片均为上海警方供图澎湃新闻（www.thepaper.cn）记者从上海杨浦警方获悉，2月23日1时许，居民陈某向杨浦警方报案称：在网上购买体温枪过程中被骗15万元。
Chen Mou reported to Yangpu police at about 1: 00 p.m. on February 23 that he had been tricked into buying a temperature gun online, according to Shanghai-based Yangpu police.
接报后，在市公安局刑侦总队的指导下，杨浦公安分局刑侦支队会同四平路派出所开展侦查。
After receiving reports, under the guidance of the General Criminal Investigation Team of the Municipal Public Security Bureau, the investigation detachment of Yangpu Public Security Bureau will conduct an investigation together with Siping Road police station.
Play2月25日，上海宝山区罗店镇一出租屋内，民警抓获犯罪嫌疑人周某，周某把自己的潜逃说成是“逃难”。
PlayFebruary 25, Shanghai Baoshan Luodian Town a rental house, police arrested suspects Zhou Mou, Zhou Mou said his absconding is "flight."
视频来源 上海警方 编辑 曾茵子(00:35)原来，陈某的公司近期要复工。
Video source Shanghai police editor Zeng Yinzi (00: 35) originally, Chen Mou's company will resume work in the near future.
由于防疫工作需要，急需购置一批体温枪。
Due to the need of epidemic prevention, a lot of body temperature guns are urgently needed.
这期间，陈某通过朋友介绍，认识了女子周某，周某称有渠道能购入口罩、体温枪等防疫用品。
This period, Chen Mou through friend introduction, knew the woman Zhou, Zhou said that there are channels can buy masks, body temperature guns and other epidemic prevention supplies.
由于系朋友介绍，陈某很快便与周某谈妥以300元一个的单价，购买总计500个体温枪。
As a result of the introduction of friends, Chen and Zhou soon to negotiate a unit price of 300 yuan, a total of 500 body temperature guns.
微信截图同时，在对方的要求下，陈某通过网络转账将15万元货款转给了周某。
At the same time, in the other side's request, Chen Mou through the network transfer 150,000 yuan to transfer the loan to Zhou.
此后，陈某多次催促周某发货，但周某一直以各种理由搪塞。
Since then, Chen repeatedly urged Zhou to ship, but Zhou has been a variety of reasons for prevarication.
直至到约定的最后发货日期，陈某发现周某的手机处于关机状态，再也无法联系，发觉上当受骗，于是向警方报案。
Until the agreed final delivery date, Chen found Zhou's mobile phone in the shutdown state, no longer able to contact, found cheated, so reported to the police.
侦查员通过走访发现，自2020年2月以来，周某经常在微信朋友圈发布口罩、消毒水、体温枪等各类防疫用品的广告，并多次向周边的朋友、以前的同事招揽生意。
Investigators have found that since February 2020, Zhou has regularly placed advertisements for face masks, disinfectants, body temperature guns and other anti-epidemic products in his circle of friends, and has repeatedly solicited business from friends and former colleagues around him.
事实上，她根本没有出售相关防疫用品的资质和渠道。
In fact, she has no qualifications or access to sell the relevant vaccines.
而就在其承诺的所谓最后发货日前，周某匆匆离开了位于杨浦的住处，不知去向。
And in its commitment to the so-called final delivery day, Zhou hurried out of Yangpu's residence, disappeared.
虚构的证件警方随即扩大走访调查的范围，连日展开追踪，并最终发现其潜逃至宝山区罗店镇。
The fictitious ID police immediately expanded the scope of the investigation, days of tracking, and finally found that they fled to Baoshan Luodian town.
2月25日中午，经守候伏击，侦查员在当地一出租屋内将周某抓获。
Feb. 25 noon, after waiting ambush, investigators in a local rental house will catch Zhou Mou.
到案后，周某如实供述了以出售防疫用品为名诈骗他人钱财的犯罪事实。
After the case, Zhou truthfully confessed to selling epidemic prevention supplies in the name of fraud other people's money facts.
据周某交代，其之前曾从事网络代购。
According to Zhou said that it had been engaged in network buying agent.
因近期发现有不少人在网上求购口罩、体温枪等防疫用品，其便动起了歪脑筋，在明知自己没有相关资质和渠道的情况下，以代购出售这些防疫物资为名实施诈骗。
As a result of the recent discovery of many people on the Internet to buy masks, body temperature guns and other epidemic prevention products, it has been distorted in the knowledge that they do not have the relevant qualifications and channels, in the name of buying and selling these epidemic prevention materials.
经查证，自2020年2月以来，其作案5起，案值100万余元。
Since February 2020, it has been found to have committed five crimes with a value of over $1 million.
警方提醒：购买口罩、体温枪等防疫用品一定要通过正规渠道，切勿轻信他人转账汇款。
Police remind: purchase masks, body temperature guns and other epidemic prevention supplies must go through regular channels, do not trust others to transfer money.
若发现经营人员有销售假冒伪劣产品或诈骗等违法行为，可以就近向公安机关举报。
If the operator found selling fake and inferior products or fraud and other illegal acts, you can report to the nearest public security organs.
本期编辑 常琛推荐阅读。
